  "name": "Oscar Mulero",
  "profile": "Oscar Mulero was born in Madrid, and is a techno DJ and producer. Mulero started DJing in 1988, and was the first Spanish DJ to become part of the Members Of Mayday. He established The Omen Club in Madrid in the early 90s.\r\n\r\nMulero also uses the alias Doctor Smoke for his Drum 'n' Bass sessions, and owns the labels [l=Warm Up Recordings] and [l=Pole Recordings].\r\n\r\nContact: web@oscarmulero.com\r\n",
